      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "Restore"}},
        "zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "恢复"}}
      }
    },
    "首次连接请先在“终端”中运行交互式 ssh 并核对主机指纹。Harbor 只安装公钥，不会修改服务器 sshd_config。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "Before the first connection, run interactive ssh in Terminal and verify the host fingerprint. Harbor only installs the public key; it will not modify the server's sshd_config."}},
        "zh-Hans": {"stringUnit": {"state": "translated", "value": "首次连接请先在“终端”中运行交互式 ssh 并核对主机指纹。Harbor 只安装公钥，不会修改服务器 sshd_config。"}}
      }
    }
